description: Loaded with barbecue sauce, red onion and cheese, these Southern-style crispy chicken pops are ideal for a cosy night in with family or friends.
keywords: Chicken dishes,High protein,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Jun 2021,Chicken,Sesame free
name: Loaded Southern-style crispy chicken pops Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 400g pkt Woolworths Southern Style Chicken Pops
0.5 small red onion, thinly sliced into rounds
1 pkt Qukes baby cucumbers, halved (to serve)

recipeInstructions.text: Cook chicken pops in oven according to packet instructions. Transfer to a baking paper-lined baking dish. Top with cheese and onion. Drizzle with sauce.
Bake in a 220°C/200°C fan-forced oven for 5 minutes or until cheese has melted. Scatter with parsley and serve with Qukes baby cucumbers.
